Example <p>entries: <pre><code>{
    {
        % #Sam# @sm
        % #Sammy# @smy
        $they/them
        &amp; is a person
    }
}
</code></pre></p> <p>templates: <pre><code>{
::@@::# ($) | [#&amp;]
}
</code></pre></p> <p>This produces this output file: <pre><code>::smsm::Sam (they/them) | [Sam is a person]
::smysmy::Sammy (they/them) | [Sammy is a person]
</code></pre></p>
